### ShopDev Translation API Tests
### Cần có admin token để test các endpoint quản lý

### 1. Đăng nhập để lấy admin token
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@shopdev.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 2. Lấy tất cả translations (tiếng Việt)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/all?lang=vi

### 3. Lấy translation cụ thể (tiếng Nhật)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/key/ui.welcome?lang=ja

### 4. Lấy translations theo category (tiếng Anh)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/category/product?lang=en

### 5. Lấy nhiều translations cùng lúc
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/bulk?lang=vi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keys": ["ui.welcome", "ui.login", "ui.register", "product.price"]
}

### === ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Cần Authorization) ===

### 6. Lấy danh sách translations (admin)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations?page=1&limit=10&category=ui
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Tạo translation mới
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "ui.test_button",
  "category": "ui",
  "translations": {
    "vi": "Nút thử nghiệm",
    "en": "Test Button",
    "ja": "テストボタン"
  },
  "description": "Test button for demo"
}

### 8. Cập nhật translation
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/ui.test_button
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "translations": {
    "vi": "Nút thử nghiệm đã cập nhật",
    "en": "Updated Test Button",
    "ja": "更新されたテストボタン"
  },
  "description": "Updated test button"
}

### 9. Tìm kiếm translations
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/search?query=test&language=vi
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Thống kê translations
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Bulk import translations
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/bulk-import
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "translations": [
    {
      "key": "ui.save_button",
      "category": "ui",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Lưu",
        "en": "Save",
        "ja": "保存"
      },
      "description": "Save button"
    },
    {
      "key": "ui.cancel_button", 
      "category": "ui",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Hủy",
        "en": "Cancel",
        "ja": "キャンセル"
      },
      "description": "Cancel button"
    }
  ]
}

### 12. Export translations
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/export?category=ui&language=vi
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. Xóa translation
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/ui.test_button
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### === TEST LANGUAGE DETECTION ===

### 14. Test với Accept-Language header (Vietnamese)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/key/ui.welcome
Accept-Language: vi-VN,vi;q=0.9,en;q=0.8

### 15. Test với Accept-Language header (Japanese)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/key/ui.welcome
Accept-Language: ja-JP,ja;q=0.9,en;q=0.8

### 16. Test fallback to English
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/translations/key/nonexistent.key?lang=vi
